data.description_en:
Groupe ROC 9321-6463 Quebec Inc. is a company based in St-Jrme, specializing as a general contractor in the fields of building, roads, and piping. With its expertise, the company focuses on executing civil engineering projects, offering various services ranging from underground installations such as septic tanks and drainage fields to drainage and aqueduct works. Our mission is to provide quality service, combining professionalism and efficiency to meet the varied needs of our clientele.

In addition to our excavation and piping services, we also offer complete project management, ensuring safety, coordination of work, as well as adherence to schedules and budgets. During the winter season, we have a division dedicated to snow removal, providing snow removal services for vehicles and trailers at heights. With our personalized approach and commitment to customer satisfaction, we position ourselves as a trusted partner in the construction sector.
